# Private board designs — real layouts + their generators are NOT public.
# The app reads this folder at runtime (see src/state/io.ts); it is absent from
# a fresh clone and the loader degrades to an empty workspace. Drop a design
# folder in here (index.json + <name>.json) and every board auto-loads.
# On this machine it's a symlink to the evedesign repo (the source of record);
# no trailing slash so the rule ignores the symlink itself, not just a real dir.
public/designs
